# Employee Handbook

## Leave Policies
- **Annual Leave**: 15 days per year for employees with less than 5 years of service
- **Sick Leave**: 12 days per year with medical certificate
- **Maternity Leave**: 26 weeks fully paid
- **Paternity Leave**: 15 days fully paid
- **Casual Leave**: 7 days per year

## Benefits
- **Health Insurance**: Covers employee + spouse + 2 children
- **Provident Fund**: 12% employer contribution
- **Gratuity**: Payable after 5 years of continuous service
- **Life Insurance**: 3 times annual salary

## Work Policies
- **Working Hours**: 9 AM to 6 PM, Monday to Friday
- **Dress Code**: Business casual, formal on client meeting days
- **Probation Period**: 6 months for all new hires
- **Work From Home**: Hybrid model available

## HR Procedures
- **Onboarding**: Complete documentation and orientation
- **Resignation**: 30 days notice period required
- **Grievance**: Escalate to manager then HR